    "Step 5: Anticipated continuation lower on the next candle open, noting SMT would have added further confluence but was not present here."
  ],
  "outcome": "Price continued lower on the new candle open, delivering the expected continuation move down from the IFVG.",
  "lessons": "A valid IFVG entry requires layered context: a sweep of a higher timeframe reference level, a change in state of delivery through the gap, and supporting signatures like failure swings or no-wick candles. SMT would strengthen the setup further when available.",
